This is an awesome series with great stunts and locations. What makes it more special is its suspense. I think if you like any other series you would definitely like this one as well. Priyanka Chopra looks stunning and performance of all other actors and actress is awesome. Love to watch it and cant wait for next seasons to release. Well created, but yes it can be improved by adding some creative stunts and ideas unlike usual for all other series. When started watching for the 1st episode, thought I should quit it but from second episode onward it gets more interesting and would like to continue.

Thanks for nice entertainment